        "description": {
            "value": "<p>This <em>+1 striking returning spear</em> is warm to the touch. The head of the spear is crafted from gold with ivory inlay and has a ruby set into the shaft. You can make the spear glow like a torch or suppress its light by using an action, which has the concentrate trait.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"pf2-icon\">2</span> envision, Interact</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per day</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You touch the ruby and hurl the spear at a square within 40 feet. When the spear lands, it detonates, dealing [[/r {6d6}[fire]]]{6d6 fire damage} (@Check[type:reflex|dc:23|basic:true|name:Fulminating Spear Explosion|traits:uncommon|showDC:all]) to all creatures in a @Template[type:emanation|distance:10]. It then flies back to your hand.</p>"
        },
